mprove oxygen delivery to paediatric patients. </p></sec></sec><sec><title>Global</title><sec><title>Surviving a mother&#x02019;s death</title><p>Lana Clara Chikhungu et al. (281&#x02013;287) review the evidence for links between child and maternal mortality.</p></sec></sec></body></article>